#: ../../source/reference/dataframe/generated/maxframe.dataframe.DataFrame.mf.map_reduce.rst:2
msgid "maxframe.dataframe.DataFrame.mf.map_reduce"
msgstr ""

#: maxframe.dataframe.extensions.map_reduce.map_reduce:1 of
msgid ""
"Map-reduce API over certain DataFrames. This function is roughly a "
"shortcut for"
msgstr ""
"在某些 DataFrame 上进行 Map-reduce 操作的 API。此函数大致是以下操作的"
"快捷方式："

#: ../../source/reference/dataframe/generated/maxframe.dataframe.DataFrame.mf.map_reduce.rst
msgid "参数"
msgstr ""

#: maxframe.dataframe.extensions.map_reduce.map_reduce:8 of
msgid "Mapper function or class."
msgstr "映射器函数或类。"

#: maxframe.dataframe.extensions.map_reduce.map_reduce:10 of
msgid "Reducer function or class."
msgstr "归约器函数或类。"

#: maxframe.dataframe.extensions.map_reduce.map_reduce:12 of
msgid ""
"The keys to group after mapper. If absent, all columns in the mapped "
"DataFrame will be used."
msgstr "映射后用于分组的键。如果未指定，则使用映射后的 DataFrame 中的所有列。"

#: maxframe.dataframe.extensions.map_reduce.map_reduce:15 of
msgid "The columns to sort after groupby."
msgstr "按 groupby 分组后要排序的列。"

#: maxframe.dataframe.extensions.map_reduce.map_reduce:17 of
msgid ""
"Whether columns should be in ascending order or not, only effective when "
"`order_cols` are specified. If a list of booleans are passed, orders of "
"every column in `order_cols` are specified."
msgstr ""
"列是否应按升序排列，仅在指定了 `order_cols` 时有效。如果传入布尔值列表，"
"则指定了 `order_cols` 中每个列的排序方式。"

#: maxframe.dataframe.extensions.map_reduce.map_reduce:21 of
msgid ""
"Combiner function or class. Should accept and returns the same schema of "
"mapper outputs."
msgstr "组合器函数或类。应接受并返回与映射器输出相同结构的数据。"

#: maxframe.dataframe.extensions.map_reduce.map_reduce:24 of
msgid ""
"Rows in batches for mappers and reducers. Ignored if `mapper_batch_rows` "
"specified for mappers or `reducer_batch_rows` specified for reducers. "
"1024 by default."
msgstr ""
"映射器和归约器的批处理行数。如果为映射器指定了 `mapper_batch_rows` 或为"
"归约器指定了 `reducer_batch_rows`，则忽略此参数。默认值为 1024。"

#: maxframe.dataframe.extensions.map_reduce.map_reduce:28 of
msgid "Output dtypes of mapper stage."
msgstr "映射阶段的输出数据类型。"

#: maxframe.dataframe.extensions.map_reduce.map_reduce:30 of
msgid "Index of DataFrame returned by mappers."
msgstr "映射器返回的 DataFrame 的索引。"

#: maxframe.dataframe.extensions.map_reduce.map_reduce:32 of
msgid ""
"Rows in batches for mappers. If specified, `batch_rows` will be ignored "
"for mappers."
msgstr "映射器的批处理行数。如果指定此参数，则忽略 `batch_rows` 对于映射器的设置。"

#: maxframe.dataframe.extensions.map_reduce.map_reduce:35 of
msgid "Output dtypes of reducer stage."
msgstr "归约阶段的输出数据类型。"

#: maxframe.dataframe.extensions.map_reduce.map_reduce:37 of
msgid "Index of DataFrame returned by reducers."
msgstr "归约器返回的 DataFrame 的索引。"

#: maxframe.dataframe.extensions.map_reduce.map_reduce:39 of
msgid ""
"Rows in batches for mappers. If specified, `batch_rows` will be ignored "
"for reducers."
msgstr "归约器的批处理行数。如果指定此参数，则忽略 `batch_rows` 对于归约器的设置。"

#: maxframe.dataframe.extensions.map_reduce.map_reduce:42 of
msgid "If true, indexes generated at mapper or reducer functions will be ignored."
msgstr "如果为真，则忽略映射器或归约器函数生成的索引。"

#: ../../source/reference/dataframe/generated/maxframe.dataframe.DataFrame.mf.map_reduce.rst
msgid "返回"
msgstr ""

#: maxframe.dataframe.extensions.map_reduce.map_reduce:45 of
msgid "**output** -- Result DataFrame after map and reduce."
msgstr "**output** -- 映射和归约操作后的结果 DataFrame。"

#: ../../source/reference/dataframe/generated/maxframe.dataframe.DataFrame.mf.map_reduce.rst
msgid "返回类型"
msgstr ""

#: maxframe.dataframe.extensions.map_reduce.map_reduce:49 of
msgid "示例"
msgstr ""

#: maxframe.dataframe.extensions.map_reduce.map_reduce:50 of
msgid "We first define a DataFrame with a column of several words."
msgstr "我们首先定义一个包含若干单词列的 DataFrame。"

#: maxframe.dataframe.extensions.map_reduce.map_reduce:63 of
msgid ""
"Then we write a mapper function which accepts batches in the DataFrame "
"and returns counts of words in every row."
msgstr ""
"然后我们编写一个映射器函数，该函数接受 DataFrame 中的批次数据，并返回每行"
"中单词的计数。"

#: maxframe.dataframe.extensions.map_reduce.map_reduce:75 of
msgid ""
"After that we write a reducer function which aggregates records with the "
"same word. Running options such as CPU specifications can be supplied as "
"well."
msgstr ""
"之后我们编写一个归约器函数，用于聚合具有相同单词的记录。还可以提供运行"
"选项，例如 CPU 规格。"

#: maxframe.dataframe.extensions.map_reduce.map_reduce:98 of
msgid ""
"Finally we can call `map_reduce` with mappers and reducers specified "
"above."
msgstr "最后，我们可以使用上面指定的映射器和归约器调用 `map_reduce`。"

#: maxframe.dataframe.extensions.map_reduce.map_reduce:115 of
msgid ""
":py:obj:`DataFrame.mf.apply_chunk`, "
":py:obj:`DataFrame.groupby.mf.apply_chunk`"
msgstr ""

